Preheat oven to 200C/400F/Gas 6.Place the butter and the plain flour in a pan to make a roux. Add the milk slowly to form a thick sauce.Take off the heat and add the cheese, egg yolks and spinach.Fold the egg whites into the mixture.Place into three greased ramekins, then place ramekins on a tray into the preheated oven for seven minutes.Take out and serve immediately.